<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to <%= companyName %> - Verify Your Email</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        
        .otp-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .otp-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9ff 0%, #e8f0ff 100%);
            border: 2px dashed #667eea;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 42px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #667eea;
            letter-spacing: 12px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .otp-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .warning-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3cd 0%, #ffeaa7 100%);
            border: 1px solid #ffc107;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .warning-icon {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
        
        .warning-text {
            color: #856404;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .security-tips {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        
        .security-tips h3 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .security-tips ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .security-tips li {
            padding: 5px 0;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .security-tips li:before {
            content: "✓";
            color: #28a745;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        .social-links {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 5px;
            }
            
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .otp-code {
                font-size: 32px;
                letter-spacing: 8px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🎉 Welcome to <%= companyName %>!</h1>
            <p>We're excited to have you join our community</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello <%= fullname %>! 
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                Thank you for signing up with <%= companyName %>! We're thrilled to have you as part of our growing community.
                <br><br>
                To complete your registration and secure your account, please verify your email address using the verification code below:
            </div>
            
            <div class="otp-section">
                <div class="otp-label">Your Verification Code</div>
                <div class="otp-box">
                    <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="warning-box">
                <div class="warning-text">
                    <strong>Important Security Information:</strong><br>
                    This verification code will expire in <strong><%= expirationTime %> minutes</strong>. 
                    Never share this code with anyone - we will never ask for it via phone or email.
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-tips">
                <h3>Security Tips:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>This code is only valid for your account: <strong><%= email %></strong></li>
                    <li>Enter the code only on our official website</li>
                    <li>If you didn't create an account, please ignore this email</li>
                    <li>Contact our support team if you have any concerns</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>"><%= supportEmail %></a></p>
            <p>This email was sent to <strong><%= email %></strong></p>
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> <%= companyName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p style="text-align:center; margin-top:20px;">
              <a href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/LDLLM1odfO9Lp1VhVguluC"
                 style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 20px;background:#25D366;
                        color:#fff;border-radius:20px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:bold;">
                 Join our WhatsApp Channel
              </a>
            </p>

            
    
            
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
                If you didn't sign up for <%= companyName %>, you can safely ignore this email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>